  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ccfef6c1cf83a9c9.jpg?v=1782536688\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>So I have a ton to share today - including the new addition to the studio right by the door - the world map cut out of vinyl using my Silhouette. I was a bit nervous while applying the vinyl to the wall, but think it turned out quite lovely. And it was so easy. I used this Penny Arcade digital file and converted the .png file in my Silhouette software using <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/37711971\">this awesome instructional video from Heidi Swapp</a>. Also, please ignore those little wispy baby hairs that are coming in. Yikes.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"19b-IMG_3392.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5787556b3fe3dae3.jpg?v=1782536691\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"19c-IMG_3395.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3853077890db7875.jpg?v=1782536694\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19d-PENNY-ARCADE-Reveal_header.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b73ce26925faad7e.jpg?v=1782536697\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Seriously, these Penny Arcade kits were so fun to work with. My layouts came together with ease, and with a limited time frame, I really appreciated that. This month, I challenged myself to use multiple photos for every single layout. Mostly because I realize that I have a lot of photos hanging around and want to put them to good use. Here's what I made using the scrapbook kits, including some photos of how the pages came together.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"19e-cheers.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e1104eaa29813997.jpg?v=1782536699\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19f-KP.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9f484e828a08ea04.jpg?v=1782536702\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19g-20140624-222616-80776381.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3a33c914ee223749.jpg?v=1782536705\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19h-20140624-222617-80777144.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/66058bbe7ee9f836.jpg?v=1782536708\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19i-20140624-222618-80778641.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bfe050277d3aeb11.jpg?v=1782536710\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19j-20140624-222645-80805901.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/057d3ae368c3107b.jpg?v=1782536713\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19k-20140624-222644-80804888.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7b3b60802763b5c1.jpg?v=1782536716\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19l-goodstuff.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c59ca0509c8eceae.jpg?v=1782536719\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>I designed the stamp set in the Spun Sugar add-on, so other than the world map silhouette, it may be difficult to distinguish what's my writing in the layout and what is actually stamped.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"19m-20140624-222648-80808998.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3a20c001f671a4b4.jpg?v=1782536721\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19n-20140624-222650-80810007.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/46e6a5c35e52e796.jpg?v=1782536725\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19o-20140624-222646-80806818.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ccb67be3fe1a15ac.jpg?v=1782536728\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19p-truestory.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/408c2f52da894f06.jpg?v=1782536731\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>It was easy to play catch up on some of Jack's album using the Project Life kits. Once again, these aren't full week spreads, as I am just approaching this album in a different way, just documenting how I feel at the moment. We went from Ventura to Vegas, and I covered lots of fun little bits.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"19q-PL.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/95db322f93607d52.jpg?v=1782536733\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19r-PL2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/df635edd5ebc88a3.jpg?v=1782536736\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>You can shop for all the Penny Arcade kits here and see all my projects here.</p><p>Keep in mind that subscribers can shop the pre-sale each month at noon EST on the 27th. Others need to wait until the clock strikes midnight tonight. Become a subscriber and get in on all the benefits and rewards that Studio Calico has to offer!</p>"
}